Merchant: You look like someone who’s been running for a long time.
You: I don’t want trouble… I just need to leave.
Merchant: Leave? Funny word in a place like this. Would you like to buy some of my magical potions? This one can make you run as fast as cheetah and that one can make you dash too far.
You: How can I believe you?
Merchant: Do you have a choice to not believe me? Here you are, running again. Tell me… when you ran before… did it end? Or did it just wait for you somewhere else?
- Buy speed potion (20 coins)
- Buy dash potion (20 coins)
- Run away